INSERT INTO Mistake VALUES('cmhnv9qsg001a2gheytde3n4d','cmhnv92z700182ghehid5u9xf',9,'rnbq1rk1/pppp1ppp/5n2/2b1p3/4P3/2N3P1/PPPPNPBP/R1BQK2R b KQ - 4 5','Positional misunderstanding','Opening','There is no reason to allow white to track down the bishop pair so easily. So it''s better to play c6 rather than d6.',1762460154592,1762460154592);
